{"tid":2433647,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［JMA控請入］JMA無視實測低估海高斯","createTime":"2021-03-05T04:31:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T04:41:32.000Z","uid":393962,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1be7a9f0a89e25d508a8d58228a170ca148f3ccc","tid":2433647,"uid":393962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T04:31:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.hkgolden.media/comment/3u2tv134.qe03qzv1lev.kp5jfbaryay.kr1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.hkgolden.media%2Fcomment%2F3u2tv134.qe03qzv1lev.kp5jfbaryay.kr1.jpg&h=391973f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.hkgolden.media/comment/n3ojtakw.kuuji1qqtsk.irl0dd3kkgc.hm3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.hkgolden.media%2Fcomment%2Fn3ojtakw.kuuji1qqtsk.irl0dd3kkgc.hm3.jpg&h=49ed4669&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.hkgolden.media/comment/okhnwq5a.5luiv0q4ybc.4e0e3vjnhi2.u4p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.hkgolden.media%2Fcomment%2Fokhnwq5a.5luiv0q4ybc.4e0e3vjnhi2.u4p.jpg&h=260041fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.hkgolden.media/comment/ifass3bc.nxa0zymjdbi.klrugxdylc0.3nc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.hkgolden.media%2Fcomment%2Fifass3bc.nxa0zymjdbi.klrugxdylc0.3nc.jpg&h=fb0c996e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nJMA繼妮妲後再度無視實測低估南海颱<br />\n今次受害者係海高斯<br />\n在海高斯吹襲當日，我save低左澳門實測數據<br />\n由圖可見，友誼大橋南北峰以及總督橋都有持續一小時或更長時間既颶風<br />\n以日本氣象廳十分鐘平均來講，海高斯於澳門造成既風力絕對達到持續颶風水平<br />\n但日本氣象廳公佈的年度最佳路徑中，僅定強55kt，相等於香港天文台105km/h的水平，僅達強烈熱帶風暴，明顯低估海高斯應達颱風級別。實際上，實測數據支持定強 130km/h，即70kt<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.hkgolden.media/comment/nynk143r.ceou1vf1exg.s3q3hy3zsby.vp4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.hkgolden.media%2Fcomment%2Fnynk143r.ceou1vf1exg.s3q3hy3zsby.vp4.jpg&h=784a2c2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.hkgolden.media/comment/13dukgiq.5od0f4xbeyi.sveslwxwrac.uk1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.hkgolden.media%2Fcomment%2F13dukgiq.5od0f4xbeyi.sveslwxwrac.uk1.jpg&h=9887c278&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.hkgolden.media/comment/hyza1mpt.tnfp4hbzcsu.kfbxmxjsxj4.5go.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.hkgolden.media%2Fcomment%2Fhyza1mpt.tnfp4hbzcsu.kfbxmxjsxj4.5go.jpg&h=19cfc630&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，澳門大學5點半時實測986hpa左右的最低氣壓，澳門大學距離中心不足10公里，數據絕對可取，但海高斯結構非常緊密（長洲距離澳門大學50公里，最低氣壓約999hpa，得出氣壓差0.26hpa/km），因此中心最低氣壓應比澳門大學實測低，大約985hpa左右<br />\nJMA的 best track 僅定最低氣壓為992hpa，絕對高估中心氣壓，低估強度<br />\n<br />\n按實測數據，海高斯中心最大風力約為70kt，985hpa左右，反映JMA的best track存在大幅低估的情況"},{"pid":"3ed836ac7f0220e672e8e6d6fc869eff7b3f12f1","tid":2433647,"uid":393962,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T04:41:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cE5CKHw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcE5CKHw.jpg&h=6305c7a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當日西環大橋亦吹超過1小時颶風<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eWxmrVS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeWxmrVS.jpg&h=b862d1fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當日九澳實測氣壓～989hpa"}]}